{"tid":1857710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年經歷過沙士既醫護仲反對罷工既賤過食人血饅頭","createTime":"2020-02-02T10:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:39:03.000Z","uid":81236,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5c1fcad91b1abb19a9587dd637bece898a5375","tid":1857710,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"正正就係因為經歷過沙士<br />\n<br />\n深知疫情來勢洶洶，取去無數同僚同香港人生命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">居然仲敢出黎拎沙士英雄光環</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地無資格同當年死去英雄比<br />\n<br />\n當年政府為既係救香港人，全力支援醫護<br />\n<br />\n今日政府政治正確行先，全力抹黑醫護<br />\n<br />\n唔止食醫護人血饅頭，仲要全港人陪葬<br />\n<br />\n班藍絲醫護先係無資格出聲反對罷工"},{"pid":"0042422d9dd1f9c5550375ea384d070cbb94428a","tid":1857710,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"為左香港政府既政治行先累死全港人"},{"pid":"92bbd59d6a355b705ba4300454e9a54910e42d24","tid":1857710,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bda10d3dc9bc269505da42ab804dc91f1066f08","tid":1857710,"uid":48868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"佢地算咩英雄<br />\n點對得起死左果班醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d7d83964343d614cbb14787806d713ef1eae12","tid":1857710,"uid":52590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經歷過當年教訓,依家眼見住正苦重蹈覆轍<br />\n係醫護都應該要嬲啦"},{"pid":"a629cf3f7e28858ccacc53d81d68944976910ae9","tid":1857710,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足裝備抗沙士：護目鏡（型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）</s